<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>XLFitness – AI Rep Counter</title>
  <style>
    *{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
    body{background:#0d0d0d;color:#fff;font-family:'Segoe UI',Arial,sans-serif;min-height:100vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;}

    header{width:100%;padding:18px 32px;background:#111;border-bottom:2px solid #f60;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;}
    header h1{font-size:1.6rem;font-weight:900;color:#f60;letter-spacing:2px;}
    header span{color:#888;font-size:.95rem;}

    .hero{text-align:center;padding:48px 24px 32px;max-width:600px;}
    .hero h2{font-size:1.8rem;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:12px;}
    .hero p{color:#888;line-height:1.7;font-size:.95rem;}

    .tools{display:flex;gap:20px;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center;padding:0 24px 48px;max-width:900px;width:100%;}

    .card{background:#111;border:1px solid #222;border-radius:14px;padding:28px;flex:1;min-width:240px;max-width:340px;transition:border-color .2s,transform .2s;}
    .card:hover{border-color:#f60;transform:translateY(-3px);}

    .card-icon{font-size:2.5rem;margin-bottom:14px;}
    .card h3{font-size:1.1rem;font-weight:800;margin-bottom:8px;}
    .card p{color:#777;font-size:.85rem;line-height:1.6;margin-bottom:16px;}
    .card a{display:block;text-align:center;padding:10px;background:#f60;color:#fff;border-radius:8px;font-weight:700;text-decoration:none;font-size:.9rem;transition:background .2s;}
    .card a:hover{background:#e55;}
    .card a.secondary{background:none;border:2px solid #00aaff;color:#00aaff;}
    .card a.secondary:hover{background:#00aaff22;}

    .phase-badges{display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:32px;justify-content:center;}
    .phase{padding:4px 14px;border-radius:20px;font-size:.75rem;font-weight:700;border:1px solid;}
    .phase.done{border-color:#0f0;color:#0f0;background:#0f021a;}
    .phase.active{border-color:#f60;color:#f60;background:#1a0900;}
    .phase.upcoming{border-color:#333;color:#555;background:#111;}

    footer{margin-top:auto;padding:20px;color:#333;font-size:.75rem;text-align:center;}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<header>
  <h1>XLFITNESS</h1>
  <span>AI Rep Counter System</span>
</header>

<div class="hero">
  <h2>Computer Vision Rep Counting</h2>
  <p>Automatic rep counting across 120+ gym machines using MediaPipe pose estimation. No wearables. No sensors. Just a camera.</p>
</div>

<div class="phase-badges">
  <span class="phase done">✓ Phase 1 — Lat Pulldown POC</span>
  <span class="phase upcoming">Phase 2 — 10 Machines</span>
  <span class="phase upcoming">Phase 3 — User Detection</span>
  <span class="phase upcoming">Phase 4 — All 120</span>
  <span class="phase upcoming">Phase 5 — Free Weights</span>
</div>

<div class="tools">

  <div class="card">
    <div class="card-icon">🏋️</div>
    <h3>Push-up Counter</h3>
    <p>Bodyweight push-up detection. Open your camera, drop into position — reps counted live.</p>
    <a href="pushup.html">Open Push-up Counter</a>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="border-color:#00aaff33;">
    <div class="card-icon">📹</div>
    <h3>Lat Pulldown Trainer</h3>
    <p>Record 5 good reps + 5 bad reps on the Nautilus Nitro. Generates your calibration JSON file automatically.</p>
    <a href="scripts/lat_pulldown_recorder.html" class="secondary">Open Recorder</a>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="border-color:#00aaff33;">
    <div class="card-icon">📊</div>
    <h3>Lat Pulldown Counter</h3>
    <p>Load your training JSON, then count live reps with form quality feedback and ROM tracking.</p>
    <a href="scripts/lat_pulldown_counter.html" class="secondary">Open Counter</a>
  </div>

</div>

<footer>XLFitness AI Rep Counter — Phase 1 Complete · Built with TensorFlow.js MoveNet</footer>
</body>
</html>
